  "text": "The cofactor signature composed of the satisfy counts of cofactors is a well-known signature of Boolean functions, which is adopted in several classification algorithms [CITATION_1] [11][13] [CITATION_2] . Reference [CITATION_3] defines an NPN canonical form based on the cofactor signature.",
